---
layout: base.njk
permalink: /work/index.html
activeNav: work
title: "Case Studies"
description: "Real before/after results from Nigerian SMEs we've worked with: short-lets, law firms, schools, logistics."
---
<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="eyebrow eyebrow--berry">Case studies</span>
    <h1>Quiet work. <span class="underline-it--mustard">Loud results.</span></h1>
    <p>A small selection of what happens when a Nigerian SME stops being invisible online. Real before/after scores. Real numbers. Real businesses (names lightly anonymised where requested).</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container" id="case-studies-grid">
    {% for cs in collections.caseStudy %}
    <article class="case-detail reveal">
      <div class="case-detail-head">
        <span class="eyebrow eyebrow--sage">{{ cs.data.industry }} &middot; {{ cs.data.location }}</span>
        <h3>{{ cs.data.tagline }}</h3>
        <div class="case-narrative" style="max-width: 60ch; margin-top: var(--s-3);">{{ cs.templateContent | safe }}</div>
      </div>
      <div class="case-image" style="aspect-ratio: 21/9;">
        <img src="{{ cs.data.image }}" alt="{{ cs.data.image_alt }}" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <div class="case-detail-body">
        <div class="case-detail-comparison">
          <div class="case-side case-side--before">
            <span class="case-side-label">Before</span>
            <div class="case-side-score">{{ cs.data.before_score }}<sup>/100</sup></div>
            <ul>
              {% for item in cs.data.before %}<li>{{ item }}</li>{% endfor %}
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="case-comparison-arrow">&rarr;</div>
          <div class="case-side case-side--after">
            <span class="case-side-label">After</span>
            <div class="case-side-score">{{ cs.data.after_score }}<sup>/100</sup></div>
            <ul>
              {% for item in cs.data.after %}<li>{{ item }}</li>{% endfor %}
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--cream">
  <div class="container narrow">
    <div class="cta-block reveal">
      <span class="eyebrow">Want to be next?</span>
      <h2>Let's find your <em>before number.</em></h2>
      <p>The free snapshot tells you exactly where you stand. Then you decide whether the after number is worth the work.</p>
      <div class="cta-block-actions">
        <a href="/contact.html" class="btn btn-terracotta btn-lg">Request free snapshot <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg></a>
        <a href="/audit.html" class="btn btn-ghost btn-lg">See our method</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
